name: Krs x Dido Brown - A Nft hussle

metadata.description:
A collaboration between million selling street musician Dido Brown from San Diego and Tokyo based artist Kristoffer "Krs" Kullengren.

The two met on Dido's Japan tour in 2005 and have been friends ever since. Krs travelled extensively with the team both in Japan and in California as a documentary photographer.

This is the genesis piece in this collection
metadata.name: Krs x Dido Brown
